(2916, 35, 'page_module_0_content', '<h3>CCCLUB Membership Privileges</h3>\r\nRegister as a CC CLUB member to earn points and get rewarded with ultimate shopping experience in CC CLUB stores and CCSHOP.COM.\r\n<ul>Earn Point Rate:\r\n 	<li>1 points = HKD 1 / RMB 1 / MOP 1 / THB 4</li>\r\n 	<li>6 points = SGD1</li>\r\n 	<li>8 points = USD1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nCash Rebate (NEW from February 2018!)\r\n(Only applicable for Hong Kong registered members)\r\nYou can now enjoy 2% cash rebate* on next purchases in the same year at any of CC CLUB physical stores in Hong Kong.\r\n*Cash rebate can only be used when accumulated points have reached 2500 (= HKD50).\r\nCash Coupon Reward:\r\n<ul>(Applicable for members registered at Macau, China, Singapore &amp; Thailand)\r\n 	<li>20,000 points = MOP500 / RMB500 / SGD80 / THB 2000</li>\r\n 	<li>15,000 points = MOP300 / RMB300 / SGD50 / THB 1200</li>\r\n 	<li>10,000 points = MOP200 / RMB200 / SGD30 / THB 800</li>\r\n 	<li>5,000 points = MOP100 / RMB100 / SGD15 / THB 400</li>\r\n</ul>'),
