(705, 2, '2019-02-15 08:32:11', '2019-02-15 08:32:11', 'Enigmatic as the new-age activism, unfettered as the modern youth stamina, eq:iq fall/winter 18 collection draws inspiration from the multifaceted fashion bandits ‚Äî the fearless millennials arching over couture feeling and street attitude as a way of life. The striking new campaign in collaboration with graffiti artist Kamanwilliam speaks directly to the insatiable demographic with an emphasis on the mix-and-match enthusiasm and the thirst for provocative images that signify individual personality and style.\r\n\r\n<strong>#britmanifesto</strong>\r\nA hint of British flair in retrospect, plaids and tartan permeate the capsule, mutating its archetypal composure and timeless modernity into a street-inspired silhouette. With a defiant mentality in the status quo, classic forms have been reconstructed to capture the juxtaposition of femininity and masculinity: oversized puffer coat with detachable knitted patterns, boyfriend sleeveless knit vest blurring the waistline, and urban trench coat combining couture texture of mini houndstooth in front. Statement is expression. Slogan is manifesto. Multiple signifiers of individuality are printed on ready-to-wear, bags and shoes to outline a new digital narrative. The line-up also includes motorcycle boots and loafers with metallic details that capture the zeitgeist of the 80s, celebrating the freedom and the cutting-edge glamour.\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-281 size-full" src="http://local.fao.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/img-press-fw18-5.jpg" alt="" width="754" height="372" />\r\n\r\n#scottiradical\r\nReminiscent to the radical Scottish colorways, the palette for this capsule is composed of cobalt blue and baby blue with a touch of acid yellow. Cuts are unexpected and imperfect, as if the garments were created in wrong proportion and shape. Enlarged chunky sweaters and unconventional cardigans inspired by the distinctive style of college girls in the Eighties become novelty. Belted calf-length skirt is styled with belted boots to amplify a feminine utilitarian grace, while balloon tapered trousers are paired with fine knit long turtlenecks shapeshifting the modern wardrobe. Along the same line, down jacket appears to be slashed with apertures down the sleeves, creating an illusion to the overall silhouette. ‚ÄòA place beyond belief‚Äô ‚Äì this is a capsule to highlight the cosmic possibilities of fashion, as well as the future of youth.\r\n\r\n<img class="wp-image-279 aligncenter" src="http://local.fao.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/img-press-fw18-2-300x149.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="397" />\r\n\r\n#westernattitude\r\nBehold the meticulous interplay between collage art and fashion: asymmetric shirt dress comes in a m√©lange of polka dots and checked patterns. Skirts are structured in pencil shape and A-line, with a mash-up of classic plaid and wool in contrasting colors. As such, a sunset palette of mustard, khaki, cognac and army green is stamped throughout the capsule to accentuate an overall Western influence. The season‚Äôs major come-back, 3-quarter boots, become palpable in accessories, of which are seen together with flowing pleated midi skirt to constrain the perceived styling dilemma. On a spectrum of oversized boyfriend sweaters with fluid fringes to doudune with exaggerated shoulder line, this collection conjure up eq:iq‚Äôs code of aesthetic: masculine tailoring, accessible glamor and outdoorsy disposition.\r\n\r\n<img class="wp-image-278 aligncenter" src="http://local.fao.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/img-press-fw18-3-300x149.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="397" />\r\n\r\n#everydayease\r\nStaying true to eq:iq‚Äôs dedication to newness, an experimental approach to tailoring is introduced into the collection. A playful knit top with zigzagging hemline draped diagonally across the body adds an undone twist, whilst an all-in-one coat mixing wool flannel and quilted doudune patch works creativity and functionality. Contrasting elements continues in the everyday essentials; putting a metallic sensation on the delicate pleated skirt and defining the feminine figure with cinched waists in jackets and dresses. Moving on to the evening, a bubble-textured mini dress, agape and dazzling, with squashy, constructed fabric of glite bubble polyester, comes in silver perfect for special occasions. With a futuristic canvas of black, grey and forest green, the workwear wardrobe is heightened by the tinsel-like lurex appearing in accessories, and the sporty attitude of sneakers and white boots incorporated in the vigor layered look.\r\n\r\n<img class="wp-image-277 aligncenter" src="http://local.fao.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/img-press-fw18-4-300x149.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="397" />', 'F/W18 Press Release', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '87-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-15 08:32:11', '2019-02-15 08:32:11', '', 87, 'http://local.fao.com/2019/02/15/87-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
