ties become novelty. Belted calf-length skirt is styled with belted boots to amplify a feminine utilitarian grace, while balloon tapered trousers are paired with fine knit long turtlenecks shapeshifting the modern wardrobe. Along the same line, down jacket appears to be slashed with apertures down the sleeves, creating an illusion to the overall silhouette. ‚ÄòA place beyond belief‚Äô ‚Äì this is a capsule to highlight the cosmic possibilities of fashion, as well as the future of youth.\r\n\r\n<img class="wp-image-279 aligncenter" src="http://local.fao.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/img-press-fw18-2-300x149.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="397" />\r\n\r\n#westernattitude\r\nBehold the meticulous interplay between collage art and fashion: asymmetric shirt dress comes in a m√©lange of polka dots and checked patterns. Skirts are structured in pencil shape and A-line, with a mash-up of classic plaid and wool in contrasting colors. As such, a sunset palette of mustard, khaki, cognac and army green is stamped throughout the capsule to accentuate an overall Western influence. The season‚Äôs major come-back, 3-quarter boots, become palpable in accessories, of which are seen together with flowing pleated midi skirt to constrain the perceived styling dilemma. On a spectrum of oversized boyfriend sweaters with fluid fringes to doudune with exaggerated shoulder line, this collection conjure up eq:iq‚Äôs code of aesthetic: masculine tailoring, accessible glamor and outdoorsy disposition.\r\n\r\n<img class="wp-image-278 aligncenter" src="http://local.fao.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/img-press-fw18-3-300x149.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="397" />\r\n\r\n#everydayease\r\nStaying true to eq:iq‚Äôs dedication to newness, an experimental approach to tailoring is introduced into the collection. A playful knit top with zigzagging hemline draped diagonally across the body adds an undone twist, whilst an all-in-one coat mixing wool flannel and quilted doudune patch works creativity and functionality. Contrasting elements continues in the everyday essentials; putting a metallic sensation on the delicate pleated skirt and defining the feminine figure with cinched waists in jackets and dresses. Moving on to the evening, a bubble-textured mini dress, agape and dazzling, with squashy, constructed fabric of glite bubble polyester, comes in silver perfect for special occasions. With a futuristic canvas of black, grey and forest green, the workwear wardrobe is heightened by the tinsel-like lurex appearing in accessories, and the sporty attitude of sneakers and white boots incorporated in the vigor layered look.\r\n\r\n<img class="wp-image-277 aligncenter" src="http://local.fao.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/img-press-fw18-4-300x149.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="397" />', 'F/W18 Press Release', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '87-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-02-15 08:35:13', '2019-02-15 08:35:13', '', 87, 'http://local.fao.com/2019/02/15/87-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
